#### H3: The Move-In Inspection Checklist
**Instruction:** Explain why the move-in inspection is critical for protecting the security deposit at move-out. Provide a room-by-room documentation checklist. Advise taking timestamped photos and video of every room before bringing in belongings. Specify that this documentation should be shared with the landlord in writing (email creates a timestamp).

