**Instruction:** Explain the process of setting up utilities that are not included in rent: contact providers 2 weeks before move-in, ask the landlord/property manager for preferred or required providers, set up USPS mail forwarding, and configure automatic payment to avoid missed bills. Note that first-time utility account holders may be required to pay a deposit.

